<p>Going further, you can implement the actual tab content switching work without JavaScript too. This uses the same radiobox method as above. To do this, include the <code>.tab-content-wrap</code> inside the <code>.tab-group</code>, right after the last tab <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> element. Then write the CSS code that toggles the <code>display</code> of tab content using the sibling selector (<code>~</code>), like the demo above.</p>

